title: 06/25/21 DPS Hour 1 Eddie Johnson

description:
Eddie Johnson tells Dan that he thought the Clippers would get game 3 because it was a do or die game. Eddie says we should give the Clippers credit, but he thinks that Devin Booker was just off and will get better.
